{"tid":2001435,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"卡列斯因欠薪解約返紅軍","createTime":"2020-05-04T13:49:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-05T04:58:57.000Z","uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"a1163a9a4cbdcc8621c8561075227c10751df1d2","tid":2001435,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T13:49:00.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports】門將卡列斯周一宣佈跟欠薪的比錫達斯解除合約。<br />\n<br />\n卡列斯（Loris Karius）今季繼續從利物浦外借至比錫達斯，繼續擔任正選門將，但經理人哥爾指這支土耳其勁旅自從去年10月起就沒有支付薪金。<br />\n<br />\n採取了法律行動後，今季為比鍚迪斯上陣25場的卡列斯透過Instagram證實已解約：「我嘗試了很多方法，希望能夠簡單地解決問題，而且在過去數個月，已經非常耐心地跟球會管理層接觸，可憎他們沒有解決問題，甚至拒絕我提出的減薪建議。」<br />\n<br />\n26歲的卡列斯將會回歸利物浦，他自2018年歐聯決賽後就未曾為紅軍披甲。由於合約到2022年才完結，所以這位德國型男今季後或會被賣走。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"5fd30d30205bae72d82372eb383ca4bcf5c1cbff","tid":2001435,"uid":16659,"like":28,"dislike":5,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T13:49:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fsmedia.imgix.net/75/8a/5c/94/826f/47f8/a279/8d9f86073478/loris-karius-makes-his-first-mistake-after-getting-an-elbow-to-the-head-from-real-madrids-sergio-ra.gif?rect=0%2C0%2C480%2C240&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;w=480&amp;gifq=35\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffsmedia.imgix.net%2F75%2F8a%2F5c%2F94%2F826f%2F47f8%2Fa279%2F8d9f86073478%2Floris-karius-makes-his-first-mistake-after-getting-an-elbow-to-the-head-from-real-madrids-sergio-ra.gif%3Frect%3D0%252C0%252C480%252C240%26auto%3Dformat%252Ccompress%26w%3D480%26gifq%3D35&h=ea95c14e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2ecbcc085e54eb41d1f70b4b48a65171a8dc8268","tid":2001435,"uid":16659,"like":18,"dislike":4,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T13:49:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://the18.com/sites/default/files/u18/Real-Madrid-Liverpool-3-1-Champions-League-2018-Final-6.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthe18.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fu18%2FReal-Madrid-Liverpool-3-1-Champions-League-2018-Final-6.gif&h=a2b78a43&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"96fd5